OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,CButtermere Bash
OL,6,FThe annual festival celebrating the
OL,7,Fbeauty of the Lake District by land,
OL,8,Fair, water, and dance is returning
OL,9,Fthis weekend.
OL,11,FOrganisers of the Buttermere Bash
OL,12,Fdescribe it as a "legendary" event
OL,13,Fwhich takes place at the end of May
OL,14,Fand beginning of June each year. Now
OL,15,Fin its 19th year, the charity
OL,16,Ffundraiser has donated more than
OL,17,F#100,000 to local causes, such as
OL,18,FMountain Rescue Teams and the Air
OL,19,FAmbulance.
OL,26,@tD@ROUtD@\O]
