OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,CButtermere Bash
OL,6,FAround a thousand people are expected
OL,7,Fto gather on-site on Friday 29 and
OL,8,FSaturday 30 May.
OL,10,FThe 'Bash' hosts both paragliding
OL,11,Fcompetitions and coaching courses,
OL,12,Fwith pilots landing right on-site (and
OL,13,Feven in a paddling pool if they get
OL,14,Ftheir landing approach just right).
OL,15,FThere is also flying for paramotors -
OL,16,Fwhich event bosses say can be foot-
OL,17,Flaunched or trike-launched, while some
OL,18,Fpilots will even be flying using jet
OL,19,Fpacks.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
