PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780063874
OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,CButtermere Bash
OL,6,FBecause of the weather, some of the
OL,7,Fflying is expected to take place
OL,8,Faround St Bees, in West Cumbria after
OL,9,F10am on Friday 29 May, if weather
OL,10,Fallows, due to the windier conditions.
OL,11,FIt is also expected that competition
OL,12,Fparticipants will fly tethered on
OL,13,FSaturday.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, the main festival action
OL,16,Fbegins in Buttermere at midday with
OL,17,Flive bands playing, followed by an air
OL,18,Fshow featuring acrobatics and stunts
OL,19,Ffrom 6:30pm.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
