PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780063874
OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,CButtermere Bash
OL,6,FIt is not just about flying. With the
OL,7,Fevent taking place right on the lake,
OL,8,Fthere are also opportunities for
OL,9,Fvisitors to partake in water sports.
OL,11,FTickets for the weekend cost #125,
OL,12,Fwhich includes parking and camping on-
OL,13,Fsite, though many of the aerial
OL,14,Factivities will be visible from other
OL,15,Fareas around Buttermere and St Bees.
